ion of refreshing, creative, fraternal, and romantic attitudes by the human soul-spirit." /></FormattedString></Label.FormattedText></Label></VerticalStackLayout><VerticalStackLayout HorizontalOptions="Start"><Label x:Name="RID_143_7_9" Style="{StaticResource basePidStyle}" IsVisible="{Binding ShowReferencePids, Mode=TwoWay}"><Label.FormattedText><FormattedString><Span Style="{StaticResource PID}" Text="143:7.9" /></FormattedString></Label.FormattedText></Label><Label x:Name="_143_066" Style="{StaticResource RegularParagraph}" ToolTipProperties.Text="143:7.9" attached:Audio.TimeSpan="0:38:10.250_0:38:20.920" attached:Ubml.UniqueId="066.143.007.009" attached:Ubml.SequenceId="143.66"><Label.GestureRecognizers><TapGestureRecognizer NumberOfTapsRequired="1" Command="{Binding Source={RelativeSource AncestorType={x:Type viewmodel:XamlPaperViewModel}}, Path=TappedGestureCommand}" CommandParameter="_143_066" /><TapGestureRecognizer NumberOfTapsRequired="2" Command="{Binding Source={RelativeSource AncestorType={x:Type viewmodel:XamlPaperViewModel}}, Path=DoubleTappedGestureForPaperCommand}" CommandParameter="_143_066" /></Label.GestureRecognizers><Label.FormattedText><FormattedString><Span Style="{StaticResource TabsSpan}" /><Span Style="{StaticResource RegularSpan}" Text="Although the apostles grasped only a few of his teachings at the camp, other worlds did, and other generations on earth will." /></FormattedString></Label.FormattedText></Label></VerticalStackLayout></VerticalStackLayout></VerticalStackLayout></ScrollView></Grid></ContentPage>